{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150731, "create_time": 1653545197, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "各有利弊吧, 纯走选调的话, 清华博硕这个牌子更好点, 其他就业方向就要单独讨论了", "timestamp": 1653545197}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150733, "create_time": 1653545220, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 信息学院不会有人考虑选调吧", "timestamp": 1653545220}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150735, "create_time": 1653545314, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 别想当然，cz就是信院某硕，尝试这条路的人不算少", "timestamp": 1653545314}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150736, "create_time": 1653545347, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 考虑的人不少吧..", "timestamp": 1653545347}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150744, "create_time": 1653545451, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "计算机系也是一个道理，清本读本系的硕博收益很低", "timestamp": 1653545451}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150745, "create_time": 1653545457, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 一心想科研又去不了本校强组的才会选择外校吧，谁能保证自己的科研热情一直不熄灭呢？", "timestamp": 1653545457}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150772, "create_time": 1653546006, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "这是你们疫情这几届才有的想法吧。以前成绩很好的保本系不出国，是会被人质疑的。", "timestamp": 1653546006}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150777, "create_time": 1653546113, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Eve: 你跑题了，dz是在比较本系和中科院的研究所", "timestamp": 1653546113}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150807, "create_time": 1653546667, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Bob: 如果只是比较中科院的话，一直以来都是本系优先级更高的。包括985211的学生保研，很多同时拿到中科院和清北的offer，绝大多数最后都选了清北。", "timestamp": 1653546667}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150817, "create_time": 1653546838, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Eve: 但是为啥呢", "timestamp": 1653546838}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150820, "create_time": 1653546872, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "但不得不说，如果你是纯学术追求的话，去中科院大牛组相比去清华一般组肯定要更好。当然，最好依然是出国。", "timestamp": 1653546872}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150825, "create_time": 1653546959, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Francis: 其中一个原因是中科院更像是工作，而不是学生。环境就一栋楼，没有学校氛围。", "timestamp": 1653546959}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150852, "create_time": 1653547531, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 这个你说错了。因为其他学校的人没有清华本科文凭，对他们来说硕士博士能沾到清华的光那是极好的了，当然中科院是第二选择。我的意思是本科清华的大可不必这么选择。本校信院大牛组优先级当然最高，但是这些名额在本校名额里也占据不多吧？至少雷系电子系本校大部分课题组都挺一般，方向也不好(指的对于cs方向来说)", "timestamp": 1653547531}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150880, "create_time": 1653547840, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 没办法的事情。雷系180来人，前35才能去好点的组，对于前60保研来说，35-60去本系强组完全就是小概率事件。其实我之前看到好像前35的也有不少去学控制和检电了，可能他们属于不是很在乎方向的人吧", "timestamp": 1653547840}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150888, "create_time": 1653547954, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re 洞主: cz猜可能在外人眼里属于降级，会被认为是成绩不够好，本系保不了研才走的", "timestamp": 1653547954}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150907, "create_time": 1653548179, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 有这方面因素吧，我指的就是这种观念很离谱，而且据我所知这只是校内部分人的风气和观念，其实大部分学校之外的人看你本科清华，硕博去中科院了并不会有降级感。相反要是去上交浙大和深研院对于外人来说就会有一定程度的降级的感觉。", "timestamp": 1653548179}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150914, "create_time": 1653548305, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 我上大学前就是这样，之前有个学长北大化学的，硕士去了中科院，现在北京工作。我爸妈还老拿他勉励我，那个时候我就没觉得有啥降级的感觉。相反要是那个学长当年去了上交读研那我感觉就会比较明显", "timestamp": 1653548305}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150924, "create_time": 1653548472, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re 洞主: 既然在乎降级感，我觉得就不要去中科院了。所谓去中科院没有降级感，更像是一种自欺欺人的自我安慰。中科院的title，可能也就在北京被认可，到了其他地方认可度真的不高，甚至都比不过当地的985", "timestamp": 1653548472}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150950, "create_time": 1653548908, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Hans: 中科院计算所自动化所名声还好吧", "timestamp": 1653548908}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150955, "create_time": 1653549049, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Hans: 确实校外很大一部分没有这种降级感觉，你可以问问你老家的一些人而不是校内的人的看法", "timestamp": 1653549049}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150958, "create_time": 1653549087, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "很大一部分人", "timestamp": 1653549087}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150978, "create_time": 1653549288, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "校内存在类似Hans一部分人可能确实是导致现在这一不合常理的保研现象的很大因素", "timestamp": 1653549288}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 150999, "create_time": 1653549535, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Hans: 计算所自动化所强组也没那么容易进，按照去年dz经验，估计差不多至少雷系电子系前40%吧", "timestamp": 1653549535}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151010, "create_time": 1653549798, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 第一，不是所有人都想搞纯科研。第二，不是所有人都想走CS方向。", "timestamp": 1653549798}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151032, "create_time": 1653550147, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 这倒是", "timestamp": 1653550147}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151208, "create_time": 1653553205, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "雷系别说前35了，前20都难找本系好方向", "timestamp": 1653553205}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151499, "create_time": 1653558773, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "建议润", "timestamp": 1653558773}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151502, "create_time": 1653558822, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re Isabella: 确实……可能压根也没几个好方向……", "timestamp": 1653558822}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151730, "create_time": 1653561815, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "同雷系，也处于35-60的尴尬位置，请问深研院有强组吗？未来打算润日，进深研院的强组是否较留在本系水组要好呢？", "timestamp": 1653561815}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151745, "create_time": 1653562003, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "Re Isabella: 雷系壬ssfd……", "timestamp": 1653562003}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151911, "create_time": 1653565393, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 13, "text": "雷系老学长聊一下吧。硕士反正都是实习刷题准备工作，挑方向不如挑没有毕业压力的放养组。博士，在保研和出国都做充分调研准备的情况下，出国肯定最优解。但如果你人脉比较广，你不妨问问上几届的暑研都找了哪，最后去了哪，然后你就会发现，其实“对出路了做充分调研准备”对于大部分本科生来说，就是很难做到的一件事", "timestamp": 1653565393}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151975, "create_time": 1653566368, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "现在雷系大二，折腾了很久也没找到“出路”……感觉时间已经不多了（悲", "timestamp": 1653566368}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153499, "create_time": 1653582538, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 14, "text": "清华在国家的认可度永远独一档，学术什么的一个硕士做什么学术，即使是私企清华也是独一档，互联网企业除外", "timestamp": 1653582538}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153694, "create_time": 1653585396, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Kate: 我知道深研院夏树涛组不错。不过没必要去深研院啊兄弟，外人一听深研院就会想为何你不去本校读研", "timestamp": 1653585396}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153704, "create_time": 1653585517, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Nathan: 其实去互联网中科院这两所认可度不错了，计算所强组这几年我知道的清华去的几个人有拿60w往上了，和校内信息学院强组硕士拿的差不多", "timestamp": 1653585517}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153710, "create_time": 1653585580, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Nathan: 60w往上我指的是清华本科去计算所强组读硕的几个认识的", "timestamp": 1653585580}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153748, "create_time": 1653586164, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Isabella: 前20还是出路可以的 。。我觉得", "timestamp": 1653586164}], "create_time": 1653545119, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653586164, "likenum": 20, "n_attentions": 20, "n_comments": 37, "pid": 50697, "poll": null, "reply": 37, "text": "真心不清楚为何保研大家会觉得留在本校就是好\n坐标雷系，感觉本系课题组很多都挺水挺一般的，特别好的实验室我承认有，但是得年级前35才有戏。其他感觉都比较一般。\n听我电子系的同学也是这种说法，电子系大部分课题组至少在cs方向上水平都比较拉跨。\n相反的，中科院计算所自动化所强组反而水平挺高的。从我去年了解的情况看二者强组都挺好，但是计算所强组其实更加偏爱招清华学生一点，自动化所强组更喜欢招211，985其他学校的，不是很喜欢招清华的人，这可能与前些年有人鸽自动化所现在在制裁清华有关系。\n所以为何大家觉得保研留在本校就是好呢，真心不理解，感觉很盲目，而且都有清华本科学位了啊，清华硕士博士学位有那么重要吗？（毫无其他意思，就是我上大学前一直觉得清华本科厉害，硕士博士就一般般了", "timestamp": 1653545119}}